snippet.title: REAL HORROR STORIES
snippet.description:
This game is based on actual events.

There are moments where the video stutters and my cursor moves erratically. Dxtory was having real issue with this game and there were playback issues while editing. I have no idea why. The game is probably haunting my computer.

It really is on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/281370/

• Twitter: https://twitter.com/AllShamNoWow
• Live Stream: http://www.twitch.tv/allshamnowow
